article_id:2512,category_name:News,title_name:Issues with the Anniversary Packs [Update],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632738300"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>The missing items have been sent around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632738120"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Affected players can claim these items from their goodie boxes.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for your patience.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>We have confirmed that the following issues were occurring between around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632722400"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1632723660"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■The purchased items were not properly reflected despite the transaction completing normally.</div><div>・Anniversary Sunlight Stone Quad-Pack</div><div>・Anniversary Unbind Pack</div><div>・Anniversary Superior Orb Pack</div><div>・Anniversary 5★ Dragon Voucher Pack</div><div>・Anniversary Facility Upgrade Special</div><div><br></div><div>■The pack can be purchased more than once</div><div>・Anniversary Diamantium Mega-Pack</div><div>・Anniversary Diamantium Pack</div><div>・Anniversary Sunlight Stone Quad-Pack</div><div>・Anniversary Unbind Pack</div><div>・Anniversary Superior Orb Pack</div><div>・Anniversary 5★ Dragon Voucher Pack</div><div>・Anniversary Facility Upgrade Special</div><div><br></div><div>We have corrected this issue, and purchased items are now correctly reflected.</div><div><br></div><div>Additionally, we will send the bonus items that weren&#39;t properly reflected to all players who purchased packs including bonus items but didn&#39;t receive them.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1632726000,update_time1632738278